nodes.text: A Rebel contact was a member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic.

During the Empire Day festivities following 0 BBY, she resided in a cantina at the city of Coronet on Corellia. It was here that that she met an unknown Rebel, sent to help her by an off duty bartender. She had an important mission for this Rebel, which involved acquiring a historical disk which she needed for a report she was writing. The Rebel had the choice to either slay a number of Imperial foes for the disk, or meet up with a commoner in the Moenia cantina. It is unknown which option the Rebel took, but he did successfully acquire the disk.
Upon doing so, she sent the Rebel to meet up with a Rebel spy named Tellulon.

This Rebel was a Non-Player Character (NPC) in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. During the Empire Day live event from June 29, 2005 to July 11, 2005 she could be found in Coronet. She was part of a quest titled, "Happy Empire Day," which would send players on an important mission throughout the galaxy.
